FY_Ship_TWS, a map by The Wormhole Studios

------------------------------------
HOW TO INSTALL
------------------------------------

1. Put the files "fy_ship_tws.nav" & "fy_ship_tws" here:
"X:\Programs\Steam\SteamApps\ (account name) \counter-strike source\cstrike\maps"

2. Start up Counter-Strike: Source and play FY_Ship_TWS !
